room_title: Escape room "The Missing Scientist" by Enigma Escape Rooms in Fort Collins
room_address: 151 S College Ave Suite J Fort Collins, CO 80524
room_description: Circa 1953. A University Professor was working on cutting-edge technology that could save the world or destroy everything, until one day, he vanished without a trace. He left everything behind, and University officials are on their way to steal his work. Find the schematics and escape before they arrive in 60 minutes.
